msgid ""
"**Warning:** The CPU in this computer no longer receives microcode updates "
"from Intel. Without microcode updates, Qubes OS cannot ensure that this "
"computer is secure against CPU vulnerabilities. While this computer remains "
"certified for Qubes OS Release 4, we recommend that prospective buyers "
"consider a newer Qubes-certified computer instead."
msgstr ""

